narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: Lots of communication skills. Meeting student from other schools.
Understanding of governance issues and the role of e-governance and open data.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: Some of the lectures felt disjointed from the projects.
I like the client project a lot

The strength of this course is that you develop very in depth knowledge related to your specific project, however, because of this, I felt like we did not widely explore more general governance questions.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Interesting topic, great organization and excellent professor
They should only take this course if they want to become involved in a very specific project.
